<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">There are certain mobs that ALWAYS see invis (orc scouts in Commons for example)...
<br />

<br />
If a mob doesn't innately see invis, your level affects if the mob will be able to see thru invis...if mob his high yellow, orange, or red to the caster then it will always see thru the invis.
<br />

<br />
I did notice that the effectiveness of the invis seemed to be tied to the level of the caster and not the level of the recipient.
<br />

<br />
...at least these have been my observations...feel free to bash them to crap =)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
